  "page": "Gunthor Goodbrother",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother\" title=\"House Goodbrother\"><img alt=\"House Goodbrother.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/50px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/75px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/100px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Gunthor Goodbrother</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother\" title=\"House Goodbrother\"><img alt=\"House Goodbrother.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/50px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/75px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/35/House_Goodbrother.svg/100px-House_Goodbrother.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother\" title=\"House Goodbrother\">House Goodbrother</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Spouse</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lysa_Farman\" title=\"Lysa Farman\">Lysa Farman</a> (as a <a href=\"/index.php/Salt_wife\" title=\"Salt wife\">salt wife</a>)</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Gunthor Goodbrother</b> was a nobleman from <a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother\" title=\"House Goodbrother\">House Goodbrother</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gunthor_Goodbrother&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Archmaester <a href=\"/index.php/Gyldayn\" title=\"Gyldayn\">Gyldayn</a> describes Gunthor as a \"roaring giant\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gunthor_Goodbrother&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>After Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Dalton_Greyjoy\" title=\"Dalton Greyjoy\">Dalton Greyjoy</a> was killed by his own <a href=\"/index.php/Salt_wife\" title=\"Salt wife\">salt wife</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Tess\" title=\"Tess\">Tess</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Faircastle\" title=\"Faircastle\">Faircastle</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133&#160;AC</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">smallfolk</a> and remaining <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knights</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Fair_Isle\" title=\"Fair Isle\">Fair Isle</a> rose up in rebellion against the <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a>. Alongside the sly <a href=\"/index.php/Alester_Wynch\" title=\"Alester Wynch\">Alester Wynch</a>, Gunthor was one of the commanders of the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Greyjoy\" title=\"House Greyjoy\">Greyjoy</a> garrison at Faircastle, composed of the Red Kraken's close companions and brothers-in-battle. While the ironborn fled the island or were otherwise murdered by its people, the garrison at Faircastle held out stubbornly. In a dispute over another of the Red Kraken's salt widows, <a href=\"/index.php/Lysa_Farman\" title=\"Lysa Farman\">Lysa Farman</a>, Gunthor slew Alester Wynch. The longships thus fled and Fair Isle was free.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Gunthor_Goodbrother&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_voyage_of_alyn_oakenfist.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Under the Regents - The Voyage of Alyn Oakenfist.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403151747\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.078 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.272 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 630/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10499/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 5740/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 999/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1542/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.180/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.45 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  263.420      1 -total\n 94.90%  249.980      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 94.16%  248.047      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.21%   29.528     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  4.86%   12.804      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.80%    7.380      3 Template:Ref\n  1.82%    4.806      3 Template:Ref/core\n  1.56%    4.101      1 Template:Date\n  0.61%    1.608      1 Template:References\n  0.34%    0.899      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:25498-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403151747 and revision